# AR Instrument Studio Walkthrough (Final)

## Summary
Complete AR Studio with **Keyboard Overlay**, **Octave Zones**, and **Safety Logic**.

## New Features
-   **Keyboard Overlay**: Visual piano keys at the bottom of the screen.
-   **Zone Safety**: Moving between octave zones (Top/Mid/Bottom) **will not trigger a note**, preventing accidental sounds.

## Octave Zones (Dotted Lines)
-   **Top (High Octave)**: Plays notes 2x speed (Chipmunk pitch).
-   **Middle**: Normal pitch.
-   **Bottom (Low Octave)**: Plays notes 0.5x speed (Deep pitch).

## Visuals
-   **Waterfall**: Notes fall from top.
-   **Zones**: Dotted lines show where to hold your hands.

## Controls
-   **Strike**: Downward Motion (>0.02).
-   **Reset**: Lift finger up.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run ar_studio.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
